Asked I think it was left one of left field staff left fields.

114
00:10:18,439 --> 00:10:39,473
That's the owner project manager firm that we have and I think The question was asked well, you know when the s the MSBA comes out with the percentages of what they're going to contribute to us and so on if the cost is still unacceptable can we make changes to the design scope now that would be in April of 2027

115
00:10:42,595 --> 00:10:43,836
So think forward on it.

116
00:10:44,256 --> 00:10:50,279
The gentleman from left field said not really because by that time you've got the design pretty much nailed down.

117
