00:13:28,765 --> 00:13:43,209
I mean, $800 million, I mean, that just to me sounds... And I think, I think if they sharpen the pencil and look at it again, if they understand what the community wants in this new facility, or as...

151
00:13:44,149 --> 00:13:45,591
updated, new facility.

152
00:13:46,291 --> 00:13:51,916
They can then begin to make, in some case, tough choice to say, well, we can take this out, remove that.

